    "\n",
    "#### Instructions:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Create a program that constantly asks user for a number.\n",
    "1. If number is even, print(\"Even!\") and break.\n",
    "1. If number is odd, print(\"Odd!\") and break.\n",
