    "- Convert result of input function to a number. <br>\n",
    "- Use some kind of math operator to check if number is odd or even.<br>\n",
    "- Check if number statisfies some condition first, then check if number is odd or even. <br></details>\n",
    "\n",
    "<details><summary>Show answer </summary>\n",
    "\n",
    "```Python\n",
    "while True:\n",
    "    number = int(input(\"number: \"))\n",
    "    if number <= 0:\n",
